trans-unit.source: Specifies the element type of the linked list.
trans-unit.target: 指定链接列表的元素类型。

trans-unit.source: Represents a node in a <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList`1" />.
trans-unit.target: 表示 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList`1" /> 中的节点。

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: 此类不能被继承。

trans-unit.source: Each element of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList%601> collection is a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode%601>.
trans-unit.target: 每个元素<xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList%601>集合是<xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode%601>。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode%601> contains a value, a reference to the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList%601> that it belongs to, a reference to the next node, and a reference to the previous node.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode%601>包含一个值，对引用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList%601>其所属，指的下一个节点，以及对上一个节点的引用。

trans-unit.source: The following code example creates a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode%601>, adds it to a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList%601>, and tracks the values of its properties as the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList%601> changes.
trans-unit.target: 下面的代码示例创建<xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode%601>，将其添加到<xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList%601>，并跟踪它在作为其属性的值<xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList%601>更改。

trans-unit.source: The value to contain in the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode`1" />.
trans-unit.target: 要在 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode`1" /> 中包含的值。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode`1" /> class, containing the specified value.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode`1" /> 类的新实例，该实例包含指定的值。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode%601.List%2A>, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode%601.Next%2A>, and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode%601.Previous%2A> properties are set to `null`.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode%601.List%2A>， <xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode%601.Next%2A>，和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode%601.Previous%2A>属性设置为`null`。

trans-unit.target: 下面的代码示例创建<xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode%601>，将其添加到<xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList%601>，并跟踪它在作为其属性的值<xref:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList%601>更改。

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList`1" /> that the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode`1" /> belongs to.
trans-unit.target: 获取 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList`1" /> 所属的 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode`1" />。

trans-unit.source: A reference to the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList`1" /> that the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode`1" /> belongs to, or <see langword="null" /> if the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode`1" /> is not linked.
trans-unit.target: 对 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList`1" /> 所属的 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode`1" /> 的引用；或者如果 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedListNode`1" /> 未链接，则为 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: A reference to the next node in the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList`1" />, or <see langword="null" /> if the current node is the last element (<see cref="P:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList`1.Last" />) of the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList`1" />.

trans-unit.source: A reference to the previous node in the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList`1" />, or <see langword="null" /> if the current node is the first element (<see cref="P:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList`1.First" />) of the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList`1" />.
trans-unit.target: 对 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList`1" /> 中的上一个节点的引用；或者如果当前节点是 <see cref="P:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList`1.First" /> 的第一个元素 (<see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.LinkedList`1" />)，则为 <see langword="null" />。
